<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤٩١٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا وَكِيعٌ , عَنْ شَرِيكٍ , عَنْ عَبْدِ الْكَرِيمِ , عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي الْبَدَنَةِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«ارْكَبْهَا غَيْرُ قَادِحٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>